===[[Season 4]]===
He is one of the many [[Great Masters]] that gather over the walls of Meereen when [[Daenerys Targaryen]] and her army appear before the city gates to lay [[Siege of Meereen|siege]] to the city.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Breaker of Chains]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

When the Meereenese slaves rise against the Great Masters, he is ambushed and killed on the streets by a mob.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Breaker of Chains]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
